egit<br />\n而家夾硬阻礙人地出入 只會變左非法禁錮人<br />\n成個行動唔legit 同塞鐵一樣 小貓三四隻塞目的唔太達到又唔legit<br />\n其實琴日癱瘓最大原因從來唔係塞Departure（要知道仲有通道留俾人自由進出），而係交通 + 有機組人員自發罷工<br />\n罷工係基本法賦予嘅權利，但我地限制人地人身自由係變咗剝削人地權利+非法禁錮<br />\n我明大家好想重現琴日癱瘓畫面，但而家人數真係唔夠！！好應該忍下手俾d耐性唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦啊！！<br />\n衝左入禁區，一陣有咩事，個單眼女義士都唔安樂！！<br />\n唔好俾情緒主導，癱瘓固然重要 但可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更有智慧地癱而且唔遭人話柄！</span></span><br />\n要接受我地係長期抗爭！其實最應該係煲大某幾日搞大佢配合機組人員罷工（呢個係關鍵），到時你慢慢塞都冇問題！！<br />\n<br />\n我地而家唔係要搞到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「旅客上唔到機」</span></strong></span><br />\n而要係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「班機起唔到飛」</strong></span></span>！"},{"pid":"2dd4cd12bd4e14d00af6fa03c15ca5f8173c2fad","tid":1461710,"uid":3822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"睇嚟搞機場真係好痛 兩日都有風吹出嚟<br />\n琴日就叫人散 散完又話自己柒咗乜乜乜<br />\n仲話聽日一定唔會再聽散水撚講 <br />\n<br />\n好啦 今朝出去又話要塞Departure Hall<br />\n到真係有班人上去<br />\n又有風吹 話咁樣阻旅客唔好<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母咩！根本做乜都有一班人話唔好<br />\n我懷疑根本係同一班人/狗"},{"pid":"86fc7f939c134ab09551de12ac5d0b161ba60da0","tid":1461710,"uid":22714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41672c1df9f5d486897a093cd7658ee372e93536","tid":1461710,"uid":25617,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>都廢鳩事上連登<br />\n成班潔癖鄉愿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:20.000Z","msg":"終於脫到P帶風向?"},{"pid":"ccde834e7ad0886deb9054efee8e83cd521564e0","tid":1461710,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"14年邊個衝邊個就係鬼，依家就係邊個阻邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52936fc585f8967218b664cd0c967feeeff3925","tid":1461710,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e305cff4bb4f2843b5cb70bc17b4ec8d6859826c","tid":1461710,"uid":73915,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"又話搵到政府弱點<br />\n原來係示威者弱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"勁多風向撚叫人唔好搞機場"},{"pid":"69a26cb2cf8a6ab2ca647259419ac53d4606d3f4","tid":1461710,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:52:21.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"5b177dc611993e67a39546ab097547227a12b117","tid":1461710,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor